      <title>维兹航空将以色列航班取消期限延长至三月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/wizz-air-extends-israel-flight-cancellations-until-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于哈马斯和以色列之间的冲突持续不断，维兹航空控股公司 (Wizz Air Holdings Plc) 取消了 3 月份之前飞往特拉维夫的所有航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/wizz-air-extends-israel-flight-cancellations-until-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:27:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
